UNICEF aims to achieve this through Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2021, adolescent girls, women of reproductive age, pregnant and lactating women and under-5 children utilize nutrition services equitably and practice age- and context- appropriate behaviours for the prevention and treatment of undernutrition.
